Make GenerateSohOtr a dependency of the main soh target.

Upstream decouples GenerateSohOtr from the default build so that SoH's CI
can produce it once and download it across platform jobs. For flatpak we
build everything in one pass, so we need ninja to build it as part of the
regular target graph.

--- a/soh/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/soh/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -618,6 +618,9 @@
 add_dependencies(${PROJECT_NAME}
     libultraship
 )
+add_dependencies(${PROJECT_NAME}
+    GenerateSohOtr
+)
 if(NOT CMAKE_SYSTEM_NAME MATCHES "NintendoSwitch|CafeOS")
 add_dependencies(${PROJECT_NAME}
     ZAPDLib
